INSERT INTO ingredient_stock_moves (
                uuid,
                ingredient_catalog_uuid,
                quantity,
                price,
                price_updated_at,
                effective_at,
                expiry_at,
                ref_type,
                ref_uuid,
                name,
                created_at,
                updated_at,
                deleted_at
            )
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $5, NULL, 'PRODUCTION', $6, $7, $5, $5, 0)
            ON CONFLICT (uuid) DO UPDATE SET name = EXCLUDED.name, updated_at = EXCLUDED.updated_at
